---
import Timeline from "./Timeline";
import timeline from "../data/timeline.json";
---

<section id="about" class="w-full bg-accent-sand/5 text-center">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10 py-16 pb-24">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-accent-teal dark:text-white">About Me</h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mb-10 max-w-3xl text-body text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
      Here are a few milestones from my journey. A curious, builder-minded path into computer science and engineering led me to research at the intersection of art and AI while exploring my creative and aesthetic voice—glimpses of which you can also see in the <a href="/gallery" class="underline decoration-secondary/60 underline-offset-[5px] transition-colors hover:text-secondary dark:hover:text-secondary">photo gallery</a>.
    </p>
    <Timeline client:load items={timeline} />
  </div>
</section>




